1. *Iznenađenje* je bilo vidljivo na njenom licu. (The surprise was visible on her face.) 
2. Ona je bila *iznenađena* što je uspela da završi zadatak. (She was surprised that she managed to finish the task.)
3. Njegovo veliko *iznenađenje* je bilo neizbežno. (His great surprise was inevitable.)
4. Ona je bila *iznenađujuće* dobra u matematici. (She was surprisingly good at maths.)
5. *Iznenađenja* su bila učestala u tom periodu. (Surprises were frequent in that period.)